{"tid":1596173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足仲咁上心睇對話會，好明顯重步雨革後塵，真係好失望！","createTime":"2019-09-26T11:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T16:41:38.000Z","uid":219007,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2689915587cdc992aaf025cf9d4c96bb4ae6b759","tid":1596173,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"根本無需對話<br />\n<br />\n沒有大台，直接民主，政府回應五大訴求自然就散。<br />\n<br />\n五年前學聯對話佢地一樣鳩Up，今日都係<br />\n<br />\n你地去同佢對話客觀效果只係俾左機會佢合理化佢個管治權，俾位佢上。<br />\n<br />\n佢肯俾手足問已經有人話算係咁，隨時化解左少許民怨~<br />\n<br />\n如果對話大會最後一個市民都無出席，共產黨反而仲驚<br />\n<br />\n竟然隔左五年又重蹈覆轍<br />\n<br />\n真係幾失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好似冇乜成長過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1a11d1fafa549997b98db83633af7c2de88047","tid":1596173,"uid":15548,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"唔屌點做文宣呀"},{"pid":"3282949c0950e290a7f6534986905c7bfd6caf33","tid":1596173,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1a11d1fafa549997b98db83633af7c2de88047","tid":1596173,"uid":15548,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"唔屌點做文宣呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"希望我多心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4b2494b39a3ac5be4e44379420d9807eff7dbb","tid":1596173,"uid":172106,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf2c18ace57307c6145be28ec66f3e3fdff8f39","tid":1596173,"uid":250586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"之前有人話抽中，成班人叫佢唔好去，唔聽，唔知佢宜家敢唔敢企出黎屌柒林鄭？<br />\n<br />\n其實好多人都仲係信對話、溝通可以解決到當前局面，皆因佢哋唔清楚呢個政府嘅本質係咩，加上無受過咩傷，又無咩損失，都唔知要點先肯停止詐瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5625434b87b581dbfe514c6d34177a449c